[normal] The High Court has recently found breaches of the prohibition of inhuman and degrading treatment in Article 3 ECHR arising out of the treatment of mentally ill men held in immigration detention in four separate cases: R (S) v Secretary of State for the Ho
[normal]me Department [2011] EWHC 2120; R (BA) v Secretary of State for the Home Department [2011] EWHC 2748; R (D) v Secretary of State for the Home Department [2012] EWHC 2501; and R (HA (Nigeria)) v Secretary of State for the Home Department [2012] EWHC 979.
